nodes.bodyText:
I always get frustrated with special characters.
@NielsCharlier can you add a test for the unicode precomposed characters which are known to cause problems on macOS.

For example, the character "ü" can be encoded as the single code point U+00FC "ü" or as the base character U+0075 "u" followed by the non-spacing character U+0308 "¨"

